headline: FICO and the Nita Mukesh Ambani Cultural Centre Partner to Celebrate Their Shared Vision of Bringing Indian Arts and Heritage to the Global Stage
summary: BOZEMAN, Mont., August 21, 2025--Global analytics software leader FICO (NYSE:FICO), is proud to partner with the Nita Mukesh Ambani Cultural Centre (NMACC) India Weekend, a landmark cultural celebration in New York City from September 12-14, 2025.
